    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Qubicks</strong> 将塔防与Roguelike完美结合，带你进入一个令人惊叹的体素世界。在程序生成的3D地形中冒险，收集并部署各种强大的防御塔，这些防御塔都来自随机生成的卡组。保护人类研究员免受一波波外星生物的侵袭，探索新发现星球的多样环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无限可玩性：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/70d0a8a1b4ce9d9e2518d62cf0929f88.poster.avif?t=1760163323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/70d0a8a1b4ce9d9e2518d62cf0929f88.webm?t=1760163323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/70d0a8a1b4ce9d9e2518d62cf0929f88.mp4?t=1760163323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游玩都独一无二！程序生成的关卡和不断扩展的可解锁防御塔、英雄与成就，带来无穷变化。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>策略性卡组构建：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/fe3b88cf5325162984aec0608e4d7a2f.poster.avif?t=1760163323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/fe3b88cf5325162984aec0608e4d7a2f.webm?t=1760163323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/fe3b88cf5325162984aec0608e4d7a2f.mp4?t=1760163323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由组合卡牌，打造属于你的完美防御策略。是选择高伤害防御塔，还是设计迷宫拖延敌人？一切由你决定。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>极富挑战的玩法：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/6282316cafb80aa7d4a06a4f5eb6f2f7.poster.avif?t=1760163323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/6282316cafb80aa7d4a06a4f5eb6f2f7.webm?t=1760163323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/6282316cafb80aa7d4a06a4f5eb6f2f7.mp4?t=1760163323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Qubicks》既具有挑战性又令人放松，为硬核玩家和寻求轻松游戏体验的玩家提供了满意的选择。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特英雄与特殊技能：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/002744c9a776c2d1e0fb70fb85d5a1d6.poster.avif?t=1760163323\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/002744c9a776c2d1e0fb70fb85d5a1d6.webm?t=1760163323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135350/extras/002744c9a776c2d1e0fb70fb85d5a1d6.mp4?t=1760163323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁并指挥一支多样化的英雄队伍，每位英雄都拥有独特的强大技能和玩法风格。从召唤元素风暴到提升防御塔效率，这些英雄将成为你扭转战局的终极盟友，为你打造难忘的战斗策略。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>动态3D环境：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在美轮美奂的体素星球上展开战斗，每个星球都带来独特的挑战与惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为什么选择《Qubicks》？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你是喜欢策略与随机结合的玩家，热衷于建造防御并适应新环境的快感，那么《Qubicks》会成为你的下一款上瘾之作。它完美融合了Roguelike的深度与塔防的策略性，搭配视觉震撼的体素艺术风格，绝对不容错过！</p>",
